Federal Executive Council has been suspended indefinitely as a measure for curtailing the spread of COVID-19   Lauretta Onochie President Muhammadu Buhari aide on  Social Media  has said. Onochie  said that ‘Council of State meeting has also been postponed; ‘Workers below grade level 12 are to work from home; All Nigerians are to maintain social distancing especially in gatherings; The Federal government will  enforce Social distancing policy especially where there are more than 50 people; 